<item>
            <title>[HBASE-7141] Cleanup Increment and Append issues</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7141</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Append and Increment should take a TS for their update phase&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Append should access a timerange for the read phase&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Increment should no longer implement Writable (in trunk)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Increment and Append makes changes visible through the memstore before the WAL is sync&apos;ed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;This depends on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4583&quot; title=&quot;Integrate RWCC with Append and Increment operations&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4583&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4583&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
